0.85 w 54 563 m 558 563 l S
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 541 Td (Member 1 Q&A) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 54 521 Td (Q: What problem does the system solve?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 507 Td (A: It organizes inventory records and reduces manual tracking errors.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 54 488 Td (Q: What is included in the scope?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 474 Td (A: Admin inventory management, dashboard, product/category/supplier records, stock control,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 460 Td (logs, archives, and backup/recovery.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 54 441 Td (Q: What is the scope of Member 1?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 427 Td (A: System purpose, users, objectives, scope, limitations, and the overall inventory) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 413 Td (workflow.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 387 Td (Member 2 Q&A) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 54 367 Td (Q: What is the transaction flow?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 353 Td (A: The implemented transaction flow is Stock In and Stock Out.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 54 334 Td (Q: How is validation handled?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 320 Td (A: The controllers check required fields, positive quantity, and sufficient stock before) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 306 Td (updating records.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 280 Td (Member 3 Q&A) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 54 260 Td (Q: How does the dashboard help?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 246 Td (A: It summarizes important inventory information and visualizes stock status and trends.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 54 227 Td (Q: What are maintenance features?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 213 Td (A: Archived records and backup/recovery help maintain and protect system data.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 187 Td (Member 4 Q&A - Product) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 54 167 Td (Q: What is the purpose of the Product Module?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 153 Td (A: To manage grocery product records used by stock, suppliers, and reports.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 54 134 Td (Q: How do you add a product?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 120 Td (A: The admin submits the add form, the controller validates it, then the Product model) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 106 Td (inserts the record.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 54 87 Td (Q: What happens when a product is deleted?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 73 Td (A: It is soft deleted by setting is_deleted to 1, so it is hidden but not immediately) Tj ET
